liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: The US survive a late surge from Portugal to remain in the competition. Completely unconvincing performance from the world number one, who ony created a handful of decent chances, and nearly lost it at the end when Portugal hit the post. There were already some question marks about this latest iteration of USWNT, there are some major doubts now. They now face a possible round of 16 match against Sweden, which, if they play like this, will be highly problematic. Tournament debutants Portugal sadly go home, after some very impressive performances in an extremely tough group.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: FULL-TIME: Portugal 0 - 0 USA

children.content: The US survive a late surge from Portugal to remain in the competition.
Completely unconvincing performance from the world number one, who ony created a handful of decent chances, and nearly lost it at the end when Portugal hit the post.
There were already some question marks about this latest iteration of USWNT, there are some major doubts now.
They now face a possible round of 16 match against Sweden, which, if they play like this, will be highly problematic.
Tournament debutants Portugal sadly go home, after some very impressive performances in an extremely tough group.
